  "remarks": "\nDIAMVILLE is an involved person under the Central African Republic (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2020 because it is associated with a person, namely the Wagner Group, which has been involved in the commission of violations of international humanitarian law in the Central African Republic, including the deliberate targeting of civilians.\n",
